snippet: On Saturday, crews tried to learn more about the sinkhole, and the county administrator said that recovery of the body of Jeff Bush, 37, was not possible.
abstract: Effort is called off to find body of Jeff Bush, man who was swallowed by sinkhole under his home in Seffner, Fla, while crews try to learn how far underground cavity reaches and whether more homes are at risk.
lead_paragraph: On Saturday, crews tried to learn more about the sinkhole, and the county administrator said that recovery of the body of Jeff Bush, 37, was not possible.

headline.seo: Effort Ends to Find Florida Man Taken by Sinkhole
headline.main: Crews Halt Effort to Find Man Lost in Florida Sinkhole That Swallowed His Room
headline.print_headline: Crews Halt Effort to Find Man Lost in Florida Sinkhole That Swallowed His Room
